Ibu pasti kamu ada sebab tersendiri.

385
00:29:04,400 --> 00:29:06,003
Ibu tak marah kamu.

386
00:29:07,890 --> 00:29:09,790
Ibu ingin mencari sebab bersama.

387
00:29:13,713 --> 00:29:14,713
